<h1>About Us</h1>

<!-- About Us Content -->
<section class="about-us">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="about-col">
            <h1>We are South Africa's Premier Sports Organization</h1>
            <p>The South African Sports Association (SASA) was established in 1995 with the mission to promote and develop sports across South Africa. Following the end of apartheid, our organization was formed to unite the country through the power of sports and to provide equal opportunities for all South Africans to participate in sporting activities.</p>
            <p>Over the years, we have grown to become the leading sports organization in South Africa, working closely with national sports federations, government bodies, and international organizations to elevate South African sports on the global stage.</p>
            <p>Our vision is to create a nation where sports is accessible to all, regardless of background, and where South African athletes can compete and excel at the highest levels of international competition.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="hero-btn red-btn">CONTACT US</a>
        </div>
        <div class="about-col">
            <img src="/images/about.jpg" alt="About South African Sports Association">
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

